  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/1bf596adb40a0b3495e99e64d72b8345.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=211 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/6937cf31aedf7c4a68bef81bf2377fd2.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=120 /></span><br><br>Bringing a nostalgic experience to ps1 era horror lovers. Enter a bizarre world and face your biggest fears!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/306f05c4a739a031c7a10be29ab2ab91.poster.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/306f05c4a739a031c7a10be29ab2ab91.webm?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/306f05c4a739a031c7a10be29ab2ab91.mp4?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synopsis:</h2><br>An empty and destroyed city, a frightening mystery, a chance to discover the truth.<br><br>Sam and Lisa are traveling by car when they have an accident on the road.<br>Lisa mysteriously disappears and Sam is taken to an unknown location.<br><br>Now you will have to guide Sam through the city of \"Red Valley\", a scary and morbid place surrounded by mysteries.<br>Sometimes evil lives inside our own minds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/ff4cb6e59bdd3858bee75f070a5f8342.poster.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/ff4cb6e59bdd3858bee75f070a5f8342.webm?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/ff4cb6e59bdd3858bee75f070a5f8342.mp4?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Game:</h2><strong>Camera:</strong>First Person.<br><br><strong>Control:</strong> Mouse and Keyboard only.<br><br><strong>Graphics:</strong> PSX graphics style, inspired by old ps1 games.<br><br><strong>Gameplay:</strong> Exploration mixed with frantic combat, First-person shooter.<br><br><strong>Story:</strong>A bizarre story with a very unexpected ending.<br><br><strong>Duration:</strong> It depends a lot on the type of player, it's a game that requires a lot of exploration, but it's not very long. (About 1 hour of gameplay).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/defbf25609f5c1c01695a0e8e0c0a8e5.poster.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/defbf25609f5c1c01695a0e8e0c0a8e5.webm?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/defbf25609f5c1c01695a0e8e0c0a8e5.mp4?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We came up with a design of creatures that were both bizarre and nostalgic at the same time. With sound work inspired by horror classics.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/f67bf453aacf7663763a99e4ed228dff.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=262 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer's Note:</h2><br>\"Red Valley\" will give you a lot of ammo... but you have to worry about your life.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/8fbc4d51ece78820482be004610fda66.poster.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/8fbc4d51ece78820482be004610fda66.webm?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/8fbc4d51ece78820482be004610fda66.mp4?t=1689298785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1978010/extras/b9c77d1c495f241831ea349045b91fe3.avif?t=1689298785\" width=590 height=120 /></span>",
